name: Gates Of Oxya - Lands By "OXYA ORIGIN"

metadata.name: Oxya Land | Pre-Reveal #1
metadata.description: Oxya Origin is a TPS realistic shooter Play&Earn video game built on Unreal Engine 5 and with Immutable X as well as Incubated by Ubisoft at Station F, the biggest in Europe. Oxya Origin will soon mint its lands which will be real game assets usable with the Dashboard which is a management tool to farm resources and craft items.
